1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 4=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=Where Is Your Secret Lover?=

4
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:28,920
(This woman)

5
00:01:29,430 --> 00:01:31,230
(has a betrothed,)

6
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,560
(dreams of a secret lover,)

7
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:36,480
(and now does this to me.)

8
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,870
(How outrageous.)

9
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,840
Your Highness.

10
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,680
How is it?

11
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:54,000
The ruler claimed

12
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,590
he was the healer's husband

13
00:01:55,790 --> 00:01:57,560
and chose to rest there.

14
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,870
Husband?

15
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,350
(Though this is perilous,)

16
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,200
(Ying Du has saved me twice.)

17
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,510
(I have to repay such kindness.)

18
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:09,190
(This is the Flame Grass.)

19
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,400
(Almost.)

20
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:29,280
(It's a hope for Ying Du's cold poison.)

21
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,800
Zhaoli,

22
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:48,680
last night, you...

23
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:51,920
Your Majesty.

24
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,520
Why is it you?

25
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:55,710
Please return with me.

26
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:57,590
The State and the royals

27
00:02:57,643 --> 00:02:59,000
cannot stand without your presence.

28
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,430
I already have my plans.

29
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:02,270
Your Majesty,

30
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,840
are you really staying here

31
00:03:04,150 --> 00:03:06,030
for a mere healer?

32
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,240
Have you forgotten your vow
to Goddess Xingyue?

33
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,680
Ying Du,

34
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:13,430
I will bestow upon you all of my power

35
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,120
to help you save the people
of Puluo State.

36
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:18,680
But you must protect my daughter

37
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:21,150
and keep her safe for her life.

38
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,280
Rest assured.

39
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,910
I will keep my promise

40
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:26,630
and guard her forever.

41
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,030
Saintess Xihe hasn't been found yet.

42
00:03:29,430 --> 00:03:30,590
Are you breaking your promise

43
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,360
by staying beside a healer?

44
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:37,080
Who are you?

45
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,710
I don't know you.

46
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:41,030
Why do you wish to take my life?

47
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:43,710
Zhaoli.

48
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,680
Never have I seen the ruler
so unsettled,

49
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:52,240
rushing about in such haste.

50
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,520
It must be because of that healer.

51
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,870
Greetings, Your Highness.

52
00:03:58,470 --> 00:04:00,080
I am a healer of the Wuyue tribe,

53
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,920
Wu Luoluo.

54
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,960
Do you know Wu Zhaoli?

55
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,240
I do.

56
00:04:11,430 --> 00:04:12,590
You're just a healer,

57
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:14,240
yet you dare endanger the ruler.

58
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:15,310
Today,

59
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:17,329
I shall take your life
on the ruler's behalf.

60
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,040
What ruler?

61
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,120
I don't know them.

62
00:04:21,270 --> 00:04:22,750
You caught the wrong person.

63
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,070
Still daring to argue?

64
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:33,390
(I can't die for a ruler)

65
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:34,510
(I don't know.)

66
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,070
Help!

67
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,720
Save your strength. It's useless.

68
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:03,230
Ying Du.

69
00:05:04,070 --> 00:05:04,910
Ying Du.

70
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:06,720
You saved me again.

71
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:13,590
Zhaoli.

72
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,880
Ying Du.

73
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:17,030
I...

74
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:19,510
I've found the herbs
to cure your cold poison.

75
00:05:19,993 --> 00:05:21,303
You've saved me time and again.

76
00:05:21,314 --> 00:05:22,709
I have nothing worthy to repay you.

77
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,920
Please, take this.

78
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,760
Luo Cheng,

79
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,160
how dare you act on your own!

80
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:29,600
You almost cost her life!

81
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,760
Your Majesty,

82
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,020
I only wish to ease your suffering.

83
00:05:33,020 --> 00:05:33,890
Your Majesty,

84
00:05:33,890 --> 00:05:34,920
if she lives another day,

85
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,840
you...

86
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,360
You're the ruler.

87
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,000
Zhaoli,

88
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,560
what happened to your hand?

89
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:48,950
You're the ruler.

90
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:52,270
So,

91
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,560
I was taken into the Palace,

92
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,000
drugged,

93
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,310
and almost beaten to death

94
00:05:58,070 --> 00:05:59,430
because of you.

95
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,040
You wanted me dead,

96
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,190
yet now you come to save me.

97
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,480
Do you find this game amusing?

98
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:06,920
Your Majesty,

99
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:09,310
even in your eyes,

100
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:10,510
I am but insignificant.

101
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,900
But that doesn't mean

102
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:14,070
you can decide my fate as you please.

103
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,590
Zhaoli,

104
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,430
it's not what you think.

105
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,360
You once saved my life;

106
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,430
now, I return that favor.

107
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,560
We're even now.

108
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,160
(Why does my heart ache so?)

109
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:10,590
Zhaoli,

110
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,560
where is your secret lover?

111
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,830
Why isn't he here to protect you?

112
00:07:15,273 --> 00:07:17,070
I have no strength to quarrel
with you today.

113
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,400
Step aside.

114
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,870
What do you want?

115
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,190
What do I want?

116
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,360
I want you dead.

117
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:32,310
Don't you know

118
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:34,830
killing your own people

119
00:07:35,486 --> 00:07:36,750
will lead to grave consequences?

120
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:38,670
Go.

121
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,480
Let go of me.

122
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:47,950
Your hand...

123
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:49,750
You're severely poisoned.

124
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:51,310
If I kill you

125
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,630
by accident,

126
00:07:52,870 --> 00:07:54,560
I could say you were killed

127
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,310
by the poison.

128
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,360
Besides,

129
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,600
the chief is my uncle.

130
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:01,800
Who do you think

131
00:08:02,950 --> 00:08:04,310
he'll help,

132
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,190
you or me?

133
00:08:15,730 --> 00:08:20,380
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

134
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:27,180
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

135
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:31,920
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

136
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:34,820
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

137
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:40,630
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

138
00:08:40,630 --> 00:08:44,330
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

139
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:47,030
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

140
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:51,070
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

141
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:53,450
♪And that is enough♪

142
00:08:53,450 --> 00:08:57,240
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

143
00:08:57,450 --> 00:09:00,210
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

144
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:06,330
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

